OL,5,GThis evening's planned 30-minute
OL,6,Gedition of Sportsday ended after
OL,7,Gfifteen minutes due to technical
OL,8,Gproblems.
OL,10,FEagle-eyed viewers may have noticed a
OL,11,Flack of BBC Sport on-screen graphics
OL,12,F(though the standard BBC News flipper
OL,13,Fwas present).
OL,15,FBut things went more noticeably awry
OL,16,Fafter a two-way with Hywel Griffith in
OL,17,FDoha, when presenter Hugh Ferris was
OL,18,Fleft reading one story after another to
OL,19,Fcamera.
OL,3,CSportsday cut short due to technical
OL,4,Cproblems
OL,22,                                   G1/3
