OL,5,FWhen a video report failed to
OL,6,Fmaterialise, Hugh apologised: "You can
OL,7,Ftell we've been having some problems
OL,8,Fwith the pictures here at Sportsday at
OL,9,Fthe moment.
OL,11,F"So I'll just continue to tell you some
OL,12,Fof the other sports news that we've had
OL,13,Ftoday at the BBC Sports Centre."
OL,15,FEventually, the programme team through
OL,16,Fin the towel.
OL,18,FHugh told viewers: "That in the trade
OL,19,Fis called a bit of vamping. And I will
OL,20,Fend it now to put us all out of our
OL,21,Fmisery. But thank you very much indeed.
OL,3,CSportsday cut short due to technical
OL,4,Cproblems
OL,22,                                   G2/3
