OL,5,F"All sorts of problems here with all of
OL,6,Four pictures. So that you don't have to
OL,7,Fput up with me any more, let's hand you
OL,8,Fto Matt Taylor who has got the
OL,9,Fweather."
OL,11,FAnd so at 7.45pm we had a pre-recoded
OL,12,Fweather bulletin from Matt Taylor. That
OL,13,Fwas followed by an unscheduled repeat
OL,14,Fof yesterday's edition of Newswatch.
OL,16,FJust before 8pm, Newswatch was faded
OL,17,Fout, as we moved into a brief countdown
OL,18,Fsequence taking us up to the top of the
OL,19,Fhour, when live news programming
OL,20,Fresumed.
OL,3,CSportsday cut short due to technical
